# Abstract
> Tired of MNIST? Want to apply your skills to a relevant issue of the 21st century?
You came to the wrong place my guy or girl - but it might be fun!
> Classify the source of memes into two classes: **Doom or Animal Crossing**.


# About this dataset
> This dataset contains **1597 image posts** extracted from both r/doom and r/animalcrossing, including metadata.
Images vary in dimensions and images were selected as best of the month in july 2020.


# How to use this dataset
> - Your kernel can be featured here!
- [More datasets](https://www.kaggle.com/andrewmvd/datasets)

# Acknowledgements
You shouldn't use this on your research, but hey I'm a description, not a science cop.
Anyway its public license so have fun (If you need a DOI to publish let me know but I'll be pretty surprised if anyone does).

Original Author, Public Domain
